# Marketplace plugin cards

Use **`MarketplacePluginCard`** (`@/components/marketplace/MarketplacePluginCard`) for every marketplace / connector catalog tile. Do not hand-roll `Card` markup on marketplace pages.

## Layout contract

```tsx
<Card className="flex h-full min-w-0 flex-col">
  <CardHeader className="gap-3">
    {/* Title on its own row; badges in flex-wrap — never squeeze badges beside title */}
    <CardTitle className="truncate">{name}</CardTitle>
    <div className="flex flex-wrap gap-1">{/* kind, version, installed */}</div>
    <CardDescription className="line-clamp-3">{description}</CardDescription>
  </CardHeader>
  <CardContent className="flex-1">…</CardContent>
  <CardFooter className="mt-auto flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2 border-t bg-muted/50">
    <DocLink slug={pluginDocSlug(id)}>Docs</DocLink>
    {/* action buttons */}
  </CardFooter>
</Card>
```

## Grid

Parent grid: `grid auto-rows-fr gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3` so equal-height rows and responsive columns.

## Docs slugs

Map plugin IDs in `lib/plugin-docs.ts` (`pluginDocSlug`). Unknown IDs fall back to `marketplace`.

## Custom connector CTA

Use **`BuildYourOwnCard`** for the upload-your-own tile — same footer pattern with `DocLink` to `adding-a-connector` and `connector-sdk`.

- TOOL cards: show **Install** / **Uninstall** (no Add Connection). Uninstall runs lab DB cleanup for `lab-devtools`.

`ConnectorCard` re-exports `MarketplacePluginCard` for backward compatibility — prefer the marketplace import in new code.
